s/2024/03/Seal-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Seal-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Seal-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/seal">海尔</a>在她的吉他踏板视频中召唤了一名电声竖琴手，视频中她正在清洁水槽中的踏板。</p><p>艾米丽·霍普金斯 (Emily Hopkins) 在她的 Instagram 上分享了一段她清洁吉他踏板的视频片段。 “这正是我清洁踏板的方法，”她开始说道，并展示了自己用肥皂和水清洗踏板的样子。为了真正“进入那里”，她展示了自己使用牙刷清洁电路板的样子。</p><p>在视频的结尾，霍普金斯透露，她将赠送她最喜欢的 Uni-Vibe 踏板之一——Eventide Riptide 踏板——告诉她的粉丝，为了有机会赢得胜利，他们所要做的就是像视频一样，标记一位朋友，并评论“这正是我清洁踏板的方式”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C32udJ_AzRv/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,